Example Analysis
To provide a real-world use case of gpu-tracker, Huckvale and Moseley used the package in their work (6)
involving training machine learning models; however, a prototype of gpu-tracker was used in the following machine
learning-focused publications (7,8). It’s a common need to profile the resource usage of model training and
evaluation to compare different models, datasets, and implementations. Huckvale and Moseley trained two types of
models, namely XGBoost (9) and Multi-layer-perceptron (MLP) (10). And they used two variants of the dataset,
i.e. one with the full amount of features (variables) and a compressed version, where a compression method was
